ZH: 大浪淘沙，唯真金不怕火。
EN: Only genuine gold can withstand the test of time.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有勇者才能站得住脚。
EN: Only the brave can withstand the challenges of life.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，胜利属于坚持不懈的人。
EN: Victory belongs to those who persevere.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有努力的人才能看到成功的曙光。
EN: Only those who work hard can see the light of success.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有经得住考验的友谊才能长久。
EN: Only friendships that can withstand challenges can last.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有真相才能经受得住时间的考验。
EN: Only the truth can withstand the test of time.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有品质过硬的产品才能脱颖而出。
EN: Only products of high quality can stand out.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有真才实学的人才能在竞争激烈的世界中生存下来。
EN: Only those with genuine talent and knowledge can survive in a competitive world.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有坚持不懈的努力才能实现梦想。
EN: Only relentless efforts can make dreams come true.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有经得住考验的爱情才能长久。
EN: Only love that can withstand challenges can last.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有真正的领导者才能引领团队走向成功。
EN: Only true leaders can lead a team to success.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有勇敢无畏的人才能成就伟大的事业。
EN: Only the brave and fearless can achieve great things.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有经得住考验的信念才能支撑一个人度过难关。
EN: Only beliefs that can withstand challenges can support a person through tough times.

