EN: Only sincere hearts can appreciate the beauty of the world.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有经得住考验的态度才能赢得尊敬。
EN: Only attitudes that can withstand challenges can earn respect.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有经验丰富的人才能在困难中找到解决方案。
EN: Only those with rich experience can find solutions in difficulties.

ZH: 大浪淘沙，只有真正的朋友才能在你需要时伸出援手。
EN: Only true friends can lend a hand when you need it.
